      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Sebastian Thrun</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/46/Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg/330px-Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"214\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/46/Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg/500px-Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/46/Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg/960px-Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Sebastian_Thrun_World_Economic_Forum_2013.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Sebastian Thrun <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Sebastian Thrun</b>,<br />\nan German computer scientits, robotics developer, research professor at <a href=\"/Stanford_University\" title=\"Stanford University\">Stanford University</a>, and CEO of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Udacity\">Udacity</a>. Before he worked at <a href=\"/index.php?title=Google&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Google (page does not exist)\">Google Inc.</a>, where he co-developed <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_Street_View\">Google Street View</a> - and founded <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_X\">Google X</a>, where he worked on the development of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_driverless_car\">Google driverless car</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Sebastian Thrun holds a Ph.D. in computer science and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistics\">statistics</a>  from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Bonn\">University of Bonn</a> in 1995 on the topic of <i>Explanation-Based Neural Network Learning</i> supervised by <a href=\"/Mathematician#ABCremers\" title=\"Mathematician\">Armin Cremers</a> and <a href=\"/Tom_Mitchell\" title=\"Tom Mitchell\">Tom Mitchell</a> from <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>, where Thrun continued his career as research computer scientist in the area of <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">Machine Learning</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robotics\">Robotics</a>.  \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#NeuroChess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">NeuroChess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Online_Education\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Online Education</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1992_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1992 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"NeuroChess\">NeuroChess</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: NeuroChess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Sebastian Thrun applied <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Explanation-based_learning\">explanation-based</a> <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural networks</a> (EBNN) to computer chess. His research chess program <a href=\"/NeuroChess\" title=\"NeuroChess\">NeuroChess</a> took its <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search algorithm</a> from <a href=\"/GNU_Chess\" title=\"GNU Chess\">GNU Chess</a> and its <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a> was based on the neural network <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Online_Education\">Online Education</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Online Education\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>IIn 2011, along with <a href=\"/Peter_Norvig\" title=\"Peter Norvig\">Peter Norvig</a>, Sebastian Thrun co-teached an online <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence#UdacityAICourse\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">AI class</a> initially through <a href=\"/Stanford_University\" title=\"Stanford University\">Stanford University</a>, for which 160,000 students registered and 23,000 completed <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>. As an outgrowth of free computer science classes, Thrun founded the for-profit educational organization <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Udacity\">Udacity</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1992_...\">1992 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1992 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Backpropagation und Neurocontrol</i>. Master's thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Bonn\">University of Bonn</a> (German), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://robots.stanford.edu/papers/thrun.diplom_in_german.ps.gz\">zipped ps</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a>, <a href=\"/Tom_Mitchell\" title=\"Tom Mitchell\">Tom Mitchell</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i>Integrating Inductive Neural Network Learning and Explanation-Based Learning</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI1993\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI 1993</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://robots.stanford.edu/papers/thrun.EBNN_ijcai93.ps.gz\">zipped ps</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i>Neural Network Learning in the Domain of Chess</i>. Machines That Learn, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://snowbird.djvuzone.org/\">Snowbird</a>, Extended abstract</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Explanation-Based Neural Network Learning - A Lifelong Learning Approach</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Bonn\">University of Bonn</a>, advisors <a href=\"/Mathematician#ABCremers\" title=\"Mathematician\">Armin Cremers</a> and <a href=\"/Tom_Mitchell\" title=\"Tom Mitchell\">Tom Mitchell</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://robots.stanford.edu/papers/thrun.nips7.neuro-chess.html\">Learning to Play the Game of Chess</a></i>. in <a href=\"/Gerald_Tesauro\" title=\"Gerald Tesauro\">Gerald Tesauro</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_S._Touretzky\">David S. Touretzky</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mitpress.mit.edu/authors/todd-k-leen\">Todd K. Leen</a> (eds.) Advances in Neural Information Processing Systems 7, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MIT_Press\">MIT Press</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Is Learning The n-th Thing Any Easier Than Learning The First?</i> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/nips/nips1995.html#Thrun95\">NIPS 1995</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://robots.stanford.edu/papers/thrun.book.html\">Explanation-Based Neural Network Learning: A Lifelong Learning Approach</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wolters_Kluwer\">Kluwer Academic Publishers</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Monte Carlo POMDPs</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/nips/nips1999.html#Thrun99\">NIPS 1999</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_L._Littman\" title=\"Michael L. Littman\">Michael L. Littman</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>A Review of Reinforcement Learning</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/aim/aim21.html#ThrunL00\">AI Magazine, Vol. 21</a>, No. 1, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aistudy.com/paper/aaai_journal/AIMag21-01-001.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Probabilistic Algorithms in Robotics</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/aim/aim21.html#Thrun00\">AI Magazine, Vol. 21</a>, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>Probabilistic Robotics</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 45, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Joelle_Pineau\" title=\"Joelle Pineau\">Joelle Pineau</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Geoffrey_Gordon&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Geoffrey Gordon (page does not exist)\">Geoffrey Gordon</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Point-based value iteration: An anytime algorithm for POMDPs</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI2003\" title=\"Conferences\">IJCAI</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fore.robot.cc/papers/Pineau03a.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i>Toward a Framework for Human-Robot Interaction</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/hhci/hhci19.html#Thrun04\">Human-Computer Interaction, Vol. 19</a>, Nos. 1-2</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>175 Miles Through the Desert</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/ki/ki2005.html#Thrun05\">KI 2005</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>Winning the DARPA Grand Challenge: A Robot Race through the Mojave Desert</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/kbse/ase2006.html#Thrun06\">ASE 2006</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>A Personal Account of the Development of Stanley, the Robot That Won the DARPA Grand Challenge</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/aim/aim27.html#Thrun06\">AI Magazine, Vol. 27</a>, No. 4 <sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Joelle_Pineau\" title=\"Joelle Pineau\">Joelle Pineau</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Geoffrey_Gordon&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Geoffrey Gordon (page does not exist)\">Geoffrey Gordon</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2006, 2011</b>). <i>Anytime Point-Based Approximations for Large POMDPs</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Artificial_Intelligence_Research\">Journal of Artificial Intelligence Research</a>, Vol. 27, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1110.0027\">arXiv:1110.0027</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i>Why we compete in DARPA's Urban Challenge autonomous robot race</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 50, No. 10</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i>Simultaneous Localization and Mapping</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/series/star/star38.html#Thrun08\">Robotics and Cognitive Approaches to Spatial Mapping 2008</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Photographing the world ground up</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/gis/gis2010.html#Thrun10\">GIS 2010</a>: 2</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sebastian Thrun</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Toward robotic cars</i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 53, No. 4</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://robots.stanford.edu/\">Sebastian Thrun's Homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sebastian_Thrun\">Sebastian Thrun from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=100193\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Sebastian Thrun</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2014/09/23/google-x-founder-sebastian-thrun-has-left-his-role-as-google-vp-and-fellow/\">Google X Founder Sebastian Thrun Has Left His Role As Google VP And Fellow</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://techcrunch.com/author/ingrid-lunden/\">Ingrid Lunden</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TechCrunch\">TechCrunch</a>, September 23, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.zeit.de/wirtschaft/2018-02/sebastian-thrun-digitalisierung-udacity-google-glass-interview\">Sebastian Thrun: \"Amerikaner durchlaufen sieben Karrieren im Leben\"</a>, interview by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.zeit.de/autoren/Z/Zacharias_Zacharakis/index.xml\">Zacharias Zacharakis</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Die_Zeit\">Zeit Online</a>, February 06, 2018 (German)</li>\n<li> Reflections on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Educational_technology\">online education</a>: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Udacity\">Udacity's</a> Sebastian Thrun, May 2013, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/uNNSRPX-YAk?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sebastian_Thrun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit sectio